name: Feeding Frenzy 2
description: Local Multiplayer 2-4, HD (High Definition). Chomp your way through an underwater mystery! Play solo or with friends to dodge predators and eat your way up the food chain to save the sea in this Feeding Frenzy sequel. Play wild, wacky Party Games. Stay alive in Time Attack! Sixty spectacular levels, brand-new fish and underwater scenes await!  There are no refunds for this item. For more information, see www.xbox.com/live/accounts.
